# OpenCode AI - Örnek Konfigürasyon

Bu dosya `~/.opencode.json` (veya Windows'ta `%USERPROFILE%\.opencode.json`) konumuna kopyalanmalıdır.

## Temel Konfigürasyon

```json
{
  "data": {
    "directory": ".opencode"
  },
  "providers": {
    "anthropic": {
      "apiKey": "",
      "disabled": false
    },
    "openai": {
      "apiKey": "",
      "disabled": false
    },
    "gemini": {
      "apiKey": "",
      "disabled": false
    }
  },
  "agents": {
    "coder": {
      "model": "claude-3.7-sonnet",
      "maxTokens": 5000
    },
    "task": {
      "model": "claude-3.7-sonnet",
      "maxTokens": 5000
    },
    "title": {
      "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
      "maxTokens": 80
    }
  },
  "shell": {
    "path": "C:\\Windows\\System32\\cmd.exe",
    "args": ["/c"]
  },
  "tui": {
    "theme": "opencode"
  },
  "autoCompact": true
}
```

## Tüm Seçenekler

```json
{
  "data": {
    "directory": ".opencode"
  },
  "providers": {
    "anthropic": {
      "apiKey": "",
      "disabled": false
    },
    "openai": {
      "apiKey": "",
      "disabled": false
    },
    "gemini": {
      "apiKey": "",
      "disabled": false
    },
    "groq": {
      "apiKey": "",
      "disabled": false
    },
    "copilot": {
      "apiKey": "",
      "disabled": false
    },
    "openrouter": {
      "apiKey": "",
      "disabled": false
    },
    "azure": {
      "apiKey": "",
      "disabled": false
    }
  },
  "agents": {
    "coder": {
      "model": "claude-3.7-sonnet",
      "maxTokens": 5000,
      "reasoningEffort": "medium"
    },
    "task": {
      "model": "claude-3.7-sonnet",
      "maxTokens": 5000
    },
    "title": {
      "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
      "maxTokens": 80
    },
    "summarizer": {
      "model": "claude-3.7-sonnet",
      "maxTokens": 2000
    }
  },
  "lsp": {
    "go": {
      "disabled": false,
      "command": "gopls"
    },
    "typescript": {
      "disabled": false,
      "command": "typescript-language-server",
      "args": ["--stdio"]
    },
    "python": {
      "disabled": false,
      "command": "pyright"
    },
    "rust": {
      "disabled": false,
      "command": "rust-analyzer"
    }
  },
  "shell": {
    "path": "C:\\Windows\\System32\\cmd.exe",
    "args": ["/c"]
  },
  "tui": {
    "theme": "opencode"
  },
  "mcpServers": {
    "filesystem": {
      "type": "stdio",
      "command": "mcp-filesystem",
      "args": ["--root", "."]
    }
  },
  "contextPaths": [
    ".github/copilot-instructions.md",
    ".cursorrules",
    "CLAUDE.md",
    "opencode.md"
  ],
  "debug": false,
  "debugLSP": false,
  "autoCompact": true
}
```

## Temalar

| Tema | Açıklama |
|------|----------|
| `opencode` | Varsayılan tema |
| `catppuccin` | Pastel renkler |
| `dracula` | Karanlık tema |
| `gruvbox` | Retro tema |
| `monokai` | Klasik tema |
| `tokyonight` | Neon tema |
| `tron` | Cyberpunk tema |

## Modeller

### Anthropic (Claude)
| Model | Açıklama | Context |
|-------|----------|---------|
| `claude-4-sonnet` | En yeni | 200K |
| `claude-4-opus` | En güçlü | 200K |
| `claude-3.7-sonnet` | Dengeli | 200K |
| `claude-3.5-sonnet` | Hızlı | 200K |
| `claude-3.5-haiku` | En hızlı | 200K |

### OpenAI (GPT)
| Model | Açıklama | Context |
|-------|----------|---------|
| `gpt-4.1` | En yeni | 1M |
| `gpt-4.1-mini` | Hafif | 1M |
| `gpt-4o` | Dengeli | 128K |
| `gpt-4o-mini` | Hızlı | 128K |
| `o1` | Reasoning | 200K |
| `o3-mini` | Hızlı reasoning | 200K |

### Google (Gemini)
| Model | Açıklama | Context |
|-------|----------|---------|
| `gemini-2.5-pro` | En güçlü | 1M |
| `gemini-2.5-flash` | Hızlı | 1M |
| `gemini-2.0-flash` | Dengeli | 1M |

### Groq
| Model | Açıklama |
|-------|----------|
| `llama-4-maverick` | Meta Llama 4 |
| `llama-4-scout` | Hafif |
| `qwq-32b` | Qwen Reasoning |

